FAD PPM 63956 QC 1953 : Correction de RespNom et RespPrenom RES.rnom respnom, --KRA 63956 --RES.rprenom resnom, -- FAD PPM 63956 QC 1953 : Fin LB.metier metier, LB.pnmouvra pnmouvra, LB.icpi icpi, nvl(to_char(round(sfb.D_CONSOSG_FI+sfb.D_CONSOSSII_FI)/1000, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),'0') factintd, nvl(to_char(round(sfb.CONSOSG_FI+sfb.CONSOSSII_FI-sfb.D_CONSOSG_FI-sfb.D_CONSOSSII_FI)/1000, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),'0') factint, NVL (TO_CHAR(NVL(round(sfb.CONSOFTSG_IM + sfb.CONSOFTSSII_IM)/1000 ,0.0), 'FM9999999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'), '0,0') stock_immo, LB.topfer topfer, LB.clicode codmo, --KRA 63956 --(select br.libbr from directions dr, branches br, client_mo m where br.codbr=dr.codbr and dr.coddir = m.clidir and m.clicode = LB.clicode) cliprinbranchelib, --KRA 63956 --(select clilib from CLIENT_MO where clicode = LB.clicode_oper) clioperlib, MO.clilib libmo, LB.toptri tarcproc, LB.pzone pzone, to_char(LB.dpcode) dpcode, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG_1.bpmontme,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_prop_m1, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG_1.bnmont,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_notN_m1, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG_1.anmont,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_arb_notN_m1, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG.bpmontme,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propN1, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG.reserve,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propN3, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG.bnmont,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_notN1, nvl(substr(to_char(cout.notif_ke,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_notN1Eur, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG.anmont,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_arb_notN1, nvl(substr(to_char(cout.arbit_ke,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_arb_notN1Eur, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG1.bpmontme,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propN_p11, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG1.bnmont,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_notN_p1, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG2.bpmontme,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propN_p2, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG2.bnmont,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_notN_p2, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG1.bpmontmo,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propNmo_p1, --KRA 63956 --nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG2.bpmontmo,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propNmo_p2, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG.bpmontmo,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propNmo, nvl(substr(to_char(cout.propomo_ke,'9999999990D00'),-8,8), '0') bud_propNmoEur, nvl(to_char(CONSO_2.xcusag, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),to_char(0, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.')) xcusaghi, nvl(to_char(CONSO_1.cusag, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),to_char(0, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.')) xcusagm1, nvl(to_char(CONSO.cusag, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),to_char(0, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.')) xcusag0, nvl(substr(to_char(cout.conso_ke,'9999999990D00'),-8,8),'0') xcusag0Eur, nvl(to_char( round((SAM.consojh_sg +SAM.consojh_ssii ),2) , 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),to_char(0, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.')) xcusmois, nvl(substr(to_char(round((( NVL(SAM.CONSOFT_SG,0) + NVL(SAM.CONSOFT_SSII,0) + NVL(SAM.CONSOENV_SG,0) + NVL(SAM.CONSOENV_SSII,0) ) /1000),0),'9999999990D00'),-8,8),'0') xcusmoisEur, nvl(to_char(CONSO.xcusag, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),to_char(0, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.')) xcusag, nvl(to_char(round(sum(SYNTH.consoft_sg+SYNTH.consoft_ssii+SYNTH.consoenv_sg+SYNTH.consoenv_ssii))/1000, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),to_char(0, 'FM999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.')) xcusagEur, nvl(substr(to_char(BUDG.reestime,'9999999999990D00'),-9,9),'0') preesancou, nvl(substr(to_char(cout.reest_ke,'9999999990D00'),-8,8),'0') preesancouEur, LB.codpspe codpspe, PI.icpir icpir, PIG.ilibel gilibel, AP.acdareg acdareg, APG.alibel galibel, LB.clicode_oper codmo_oper, nvl(to_char(round((sfb.M_CONSOSG_FI + sfb.M_CONSOSSII_FI)/1000) , 'FM999999999990D00','NLS_NUMERIC_CHARACTERS='',.'),'0,0') CoûtMM, LB.sous_type sous_typo, replace(replace( replace( nvl(to_char(LB.POBJET),' ' ) , CHR(10) , ' ' ), ' ',' '), ';', ',') pobjet,
--Ajout dans le cadre de la PPM 62334 paragraphe 6.9 par FAD --BIP 32 CHANGES START PACK_ARBITRE.FIND_REF_DEMANDE(NULL,DPCOPI.DPCOPIAXEMETIER,PI.PROJAXEMETIER,LB.PID) Ref_demande, PACK_ARBITRE.FIND_REF_DEMANDE_LIB(DPCOPI.DPCOPIAXEMETIER,PI.PROJAXEMETIER,LB.PID) Ref_demande_Lib, --BIP 32 CHANGES DONE DPCOPI.DPCOPIAXEMETIER DpCopiAxeMetierCode, DECODE ( DPCOPI.DPCOPIAXEMETIER , NULL , ' ' , DECODE ( ( SELECT DMPLIBEL FROM DMP_RESEAUXFRANCE WHERE TRIM ( DMPNUM ) = TRIM ( DPCOPI.DPCOPIAXEMETIER ) AND ROWNUM = 1 ) , NULL , '???' , ( SELECT DMPLIBEL FROM DMP_RESEAUXFRANCE WHERE TRIM ( DMPNUM ) = TRIM ( DPCOPI.DPCOPIAXEMETIER ) AND ROWNUM = 1 ) ) ) DpCopiAxeMetierLib, PI.PROJAXEMETIER ProjAxeMetierCode , DECODE ( PI.PROJAXEMETIER , NULL , ' ' , DECODE ( ( SELECT DMPLIBEL FROM DMP_RESEAUXFRANCE WHERE TRIM ( DMPNUM ) = TRIM ( PI.PROJAXEMETIER ) AND ROWNUM = 1 ) , NULL , '???' , ( SELECT DMPLIBEL FROM DMP_RESEAUXFRANCE WHERE TRIM ( DMPNUM ) = TRIM ( PI.PROJAXEMETIER ) AND ROWNUM = 1 ) ) ) ProjAxeMetierLib --Fin
FROM CONSOMME CONSO, CONSOMME CONSO_1, CONSOMME CONSO_2, BUDGET BUDG, --table des budgets pour l'année en cours BUDGET BUDG_1, --table des budgets pour l'année en cours-1 BUDGET BUDG1, --table des budgets pour l'année en cours+1 BUDGET BUDG2, --table des budgets pour l'année en cours+2 BUDGET BUDG3, --table des budgets pour l'année en cours+3 LIGNE_BIP LB, DATDEBEX, APPLICATION AP, PROJ_INFO PI, STRUCT_INFO SI, DIRECTIONS DIR, BRANCHES BR, RESSOURCE RES, CLIENT_MO MO, PROJ_INFO PIG, DOSSIER_PROJET DP, DOSSIER_PROJET_COPI DPCOPI, APPLICATION APG, SYNTHESE_ACTIVITE_MOIS SAM, SYNTHESE_ACTIVITE SYNTH, SYNTHESE_FIN_BIP SFB, TMP_COUTKE_ETATS cout --ISAC_TACHE ita, isac_sous_tache isst, isac_etape iet WHERE -- jointures LB.pid = CONSO.pid(+) AND LB.pid = CONSO_1.pid(+) AND LB.pid = CONSO_2.pid(+) AND LB.pid = SFB.pid(+) AND LB.pid = SAM.pid (+) AND LB.pid = BUDG.pid(+) AND LB.pid = BUDG_1.pid(+) AND LB.pid = BUDG1.pid(+) AND LB.pid = BUDG2.pid(+) AND LB.pid = BUDG3.pid(+) AND LB.pid = SYNTH.pid(+) AND BUDG.annee(+) = :P_ANNEE AND BUDG_1.annee(+) = :P_ANNEE-1 AND BUDG1.annee(+) = :P_ANNEE+1 AND BUDG2.annee(+) = :P_ANNEE+2 AND BUDG3.annee(+) = :P_ANNEE+3 AND CONSO.annee (+) = :P_ANNEE AND CONSO_1.annee (+) = :P_ANNEE-1 AND CONSO_2.annee (+) = :P_ANNEE-2 AND SAM.cdeb(+) = :P_MOISMENS AND SFB.annee(+) = :P_ANNEE AND LB.icpi = PI.icpi(+) AND LB.codsg = SI.codsg(+) AND SI.coddir = DIR.coddir(+) --KRA 63956 -- FAD PPM 63956 QC 1954 : Ajout du (+) à BR.CODBR AND BR.CODBR(+) = DIR.CODBR -- FAD PPM 63956 QC 1954 : Fin AND LB.pcpi = RES.ident(+) AND LB.clicode = MO.clicode(+) AND LB.airt = AP.airt(+) AND LB.dpcode = DP.dpcode(+) AND PI.dp_copi = DPCOPI.dp_copi(+) AND PI.icpir = PIG.icpi(+) AND AP.acdareg = APG.airt(+) AND cout.pid(+) = LB.pid AND cout.codsg(+) = LB.codsg AND cout.metier(+) = LB.metier AND cout.numseq(+) = :P_NUMSEQ AND (extract (YEAR FROM LB.ADATESTATUT) >= :P_ANNEE OR LB.adatestatut IS NULL) --and isst.pid = lb.pid --AND isst.etape = iet.etape --AND isst.tache = ita.tache --AND DPCOPI.dp_copi(+) = PI.dp_copi
AND (EXISTS (SELECT CLICODE FROM CLICODE_RBDF WHERE CLICODE = LB.CLICODE) OR EXISTS (SELECT CODSG FROM CODSG_RBDF WHERE CODSG = LB.CODSG))
group by LB.pid,LB.pnom, LB.codsg,LB.typproj,SI.libdsg,DIR.libdir,BR.libbr,LB.codcamo,LB.arctype,LB.pcpi,res.rnom,res.rprenom,LB.metier,LB.pnmouvra,LB.icpi,PI.ilibel,LB.airt,AP.alibel,DP.dplib,PI.dp_copi, DPCOPI.libelle,LB.astatut,LB.adatestatut,sfb.D_CONSOSG_FI,D_CONSOSSII_FI,sfb.CONSOSG_FI,CONSOSSII_FI, sfb.CONSOFTSG_IM,sfb.CONSOFTSSII_IM,LB.topfer,LB.clicode,MO.clilib,LB.toptri,LB.pzone,LB.dpcode,BUDG_1.bpmontme,BUDG_1.bnmont,BUDG_1.anmont,BUDG.bpmontme, BUDG.reserve,BUDG.bnmont,cout.notif_ke,BUDG.anmont,cout.arbit_ke,BUDG1.bpmontme,BUDG1.bnmont,BUDG2.bpmontme,BUDG2.bnmont,BUDG1.bpmontmo,BUDG2.bpmontmo,BUDG.bpmontmo, cout.propomo_ke,CONSO_2.xcusag,CONSO_1.cusag,CONSO.cusag,cout.conso_ke,SAM.consojh_sg,SAM.consojh_ssii,SAM.CONSOFT_SG,SAM.CONSOFT_SSII,SAM.CONSOENV_SG,SAM.CONSOENV_SSII, CONSO.xcusag,BUDG.reestime,cout.reest_ke,LB.codpspe,PI.icpir,PIG.ilibel,AP.acdareg,APG.alibel,LB.clicode_oper,sfb.M_CONSOSG_FI,sfb.M_CONSOSSII_FI,LB.sous_type,LB.POBJET, DPCOPI.DPCOPIAXEMETIER,PI.PROJAXEMETIER--,LB.LINEAXISBUSINESS2,ITA.TACHEAXEMETIER ORDER BY LB.adatestatut;
